Package: power4ctl
Version: @VERSION@
Architecture: @ARCH@
Maintainer: Jim Studt <jim@studt.net>
Depends: libc6
Section: utils
Priority: optional
Description: Serial management tool for the power4 ESP32 device
 Command-line tool for querying and managing a power4 ESP32 controller
 over its serial console. Supports JSON state reports for batteries,
 battery banks, and relays, policy program upload, and general-purpose
 passthrough access to the device console.
